When the Shop Owner will open the software, a welcome page asking the user id
and password will be displayed. Upon logging in, the software will display four
buttons along with a billing button and an exit button. The four functionalities
include, Stocks, Sales, Requires Parts, Add parts. The stocks button will show the
list of current stock of motor parts. The sales button will display the sales statistics
of the shop. Upon the clicking the exit button, the current user will be logged out
and the login page will be displayed again. The billing button will direct the user to
the billing page. The requires parts button will display the motor parts that need to
be restocked by the end of the day.The add parts page will help in adding the
recent number of restocked motor parts. The UI is kept simple and understandable
for the user, so that it can work with it without hassle.

